{"slug":"ancient-legends","title":{"en":"Ancient Legends","km":"ព្រេងនិទានបុរាណ"},"description":{"en":"The story is based on classic Chinese mythology and the ancient text Shan Hai Jing. It follows the Flower Goddess (the Jade Emperor's younger sister) and Shennong as they travel across the land to find a cure for a mysterious plague. The drama features legendary events like Nüwa repairing the sky and Houyi shooting down the nine suns, exploring the origins of Chinese civilization and the struggle between gods and demons.","km":"សាច់រឿងនេះត្រូវបានដកស្រង់ចេញពីទេវកថាចិនបុរាណ និងគម្ពីរ Shan Hai Jing។ រឿងនេះនិយាយពីដំណើរផ្សងព្រេងរបស់ ព្រះនាងបុប្ផា (ប្អូនស្រីរបស់ព្រះឥន្ទ) និងលោក សិនណុង (Shennong) ក្នុងការស្វែងរកថ្នាំព្យាបាលជំងឺអាសន្នរោគដែលកំពុងយាយីមនុស្សលោក។ ក្នុងរឿងនេះ ក៏មានបញ្ចូលនូវព្រឹត្តិការណ៍ល្បីៗដូចជា៖ ព្រះនាងនីវ៉ាជួសជុលមេឃ និង ហូវអ៊ី បាញ់ទម្លាក់ព្រះអាទិត្យទាំង៩ ដើម្បីសង្គ្រោះពិភពលោកផងដែរ។"},"poster":"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgacSTct2SdppokhpmDOUetrV56Kw-IB0SDbc3CK_TweUYjs13U7dRJAkJHKB9TI1hMDz0dGZRGgJr5-g9J3RuVHtN37t1Jxkz0x2P0IDRcRb1BYl_QCh5n-n2dSd-1iuiq2sYJKhEZ83aJmP7AS4e-CbiAWHDYPf54LiGHHWuyP3jYyi7TAa8Y9KaLV8ih/s16000/am.jpg","year":2010,"rating":7.5,"genres":["FANTASY","ROMANCE"],"language":"English","episodeCount":54,"episodes":[{"ep":"1","title":{"en":"Episode 1","km":"ភាគទី1"},"url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ipro855/em/refs/heads/an1/x/index.single","type":"M3U8","final":false},{"ep":"2","title":{"en":"Episode 2","km":"ភាគទី2"},"url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ipro855/em/refs/heads/an2/x/index.single","type":"M3U8","final":false},{"ep":"3","title":{"en":"Episode 3","km":"ភាគទី3"},"url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ipro855/em/refs/heads/an3/x/index.single","type":"M3U8","final":false},{"ep":"4","title":{"en":"Episode 4","km":"ភាគទី4"},"url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ipro855/em/refs/heads/an4/x/index.single","type":"M3U8","final":false},{"ep":"5","title":{"en":"Episode 5","km":"ភាគទី5"},"url":"htt